tipc: Fix recognition of trial period

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v4.19.264 by commit d62e0f037e482f2fbb671496a797ff807f292dd6, it was introduced in version v4.18 by commit e415577f57f4452150642500364cbe5fa6112813. For more details please see the references link.
